OL,4,G1055FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GSimon and his friend Shirley host
OL,6,     Gat The Old Hall Country House in
OL,7,     GMadeley, Cheshire. Their guests
OL,8,     Gare in awe of the 16th-century
OL,9,     Gbuilding, and are treated to tap
OL,10,     Gdancing and fine dining.
OL,11,G1125FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GCat-lover Eileen Finn welcomes
OL,13,     Gher rivals to the four-star
OL,14,     GThornley House in Allendale,
OL,15,     GNorthumberland. But Eileen's
OL,16,     Gbeloved and very large cats are
OL,17,     Gnot to all of her guests' liking.
