OL,4,G1155FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GJessica and Adrian Rashleigh hope
OL,6,     Gthat the beautiful Cornish
OL,7,     Gcoastal surroundings will make up
OL,8,     Gfor the snugness of the three-
OL,9,     Gbedroom Chy Conyn in St Ives.
OL,10,     GWill their guests agree?
OL,11,G1230FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe final hosts are Tim and Karen
OL,13,     Gat The Cavendish, where
OL,14,     Gactivities include a bus tour of
OL,15,     GBournemouth. The 'pink palace'
OL,16,     Gimpresses their guests, but Simon
OL,17,     Gand Shirley break their bed.
