OL,4,G1300FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GIt's the final day of the
OL,6,     Gcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,7,     Gone last time to see how much
OL,8,     Gthey've been paid. After a
OL,9,     Ggenerous overpayment and some
OL,10,     Gharsh criticism, the winner is
OL,11,     Gannounced.
