OL,11,G0010FEmergency Helicopter Medics
OL,12,     GThe helicopter medics battle bad
OL,13,     Gweather in Cumbria to reach
OL,14,     Ginjured 70-year-old hill-walker
OL,15,     GJenny. Meanwhile, biker Ronald
OL,16,     Gneeds urgent treatment after a
OL,17,     Gcrash.
